summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting deeds to a portion of Tract 129, West Seattle Five Acre Tracts No. 4, and a portion of Tract 5, Prospect Tracts for street purposes and laying off 52nd Place Southwest and 35th Avenue Southwest (Street Dedication 52nd Place Southwest North of Southwest Dakota Street; Street Vacation 35th Avenue Southwest at Southwest Admiral Way, C.F. 283982).
